m е°ҫйғЁ `-`\\n- [ ] T-002.03 дёӨдёӘ helper еқҮеҢ…еҗ«жіЁйҮҠж–ҮжЎЈпјҲз”ЁйҖ”гҖҒиҫ“е…ҘгҖҒиҫ“еҮәпјү\\n\\n**йӘҢж”¶**: `helm template test manifests/charts/base` ж— жЁЎжқҝжёІжҹ“й”ҷиҜҜпјӣhelper е®ҡд№үиҜӯжі•жӯЈзЎ®\\n\\n---\\n\\n## T-003: WorkloadManager RBAC жЁЎжқҝж”№йҖ \\n\\n- [ ] T-003.01 еңЁж–Үд»¶йЎ¶йғЁж·»еҠ  `{{- $_ := set . \\\"componentName\\\" \\\"workloadmanager\\\" }}`\\n- [ ] T-003.02 ж•ҙдёӘж–Үд»¶еҢ…иЈ№еңЁ `{{- if .Values.workloadmanager.rbac.create }}` / `{{- end }}` дёӯ\\n- [ ] T-003.03 ServiceAccount labels жӣҝжҚўдёә `{{- include \\\"agentcube.labels\\\" . | nindent 4 }}` + `app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager` + `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac`\\n- [ ] T-003.04 Cluste...\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775873714603,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a5247b8001zMEuSdTjzD3Jt2\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a522465001yPtfEWwvz0jANs\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285b351c9ffeisKLz4DZy8C60B\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The LSP errors are false positives вҖ” they're treating Helm template files (containing `{{ }}` Go template syntax) as pure YAML. This is expected and not an issue with the tasks.md.\\n\\nWritten `changes/AR-031/tasks.md` with 16 atomic tasks (T-001 through T-016) organized into 5 parallelizable groups:\\n\\n| Group | Tasks | Description |\\n|-------|-------|-------------|\\n| G1 | T-001 | values.yaml RBAC keys |\\n| G2 | T-002 | _helpers.tpl RBAC helpers |\\n| G3 | T-003, T-004, T-006 | Three RBAC templates (parallel) |\\n| G4 | T-005, T-007 | Delete old file + strip Volcano template |\\n| G5 | T-008вҖ“T-016 | All verification tasks (parallel) |\\n\\n22 acceptance criteria (AC1вҖ“AC22) with verifiable commands.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775873714601,\"end\":1775873714601}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-031_ST-4.log:\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872674812,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a42802e001QV9g7YG32XW080\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a426f9c001UR4aJjKHNkADxz\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_19863721b0424a36bff0bf8b\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/manifests/agentcube/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/manifests/agentcube/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-031 вҖ” RBAC Configuration (SA/Role/Binding)\\n2: \\n3: - **AR ID**: AR-031\\n4: - **Module**: manifests\\n5: - **Language**: YAML (Helm)\\n6: - **Size**: M\\n7: - **Status**: ST-1 Completed (design.md)\\n8: \\n9: ## 1. Architecture\\n10: \\n11: ### 1.1 Overview\\n12: \\n13: The RBAC (Role-Based Access Control) configuration for AgentCube provides fine-grained permission management using Kubernetes native RBAC primitives. The implementation follows the standard Kubernetes RBAC model with ServiceAccount, Role/ClusterRole, and RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding resources.\\n14: \\n15: ### 1.2 RBAC Components\\n16: \\n17: ```\\n18: в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\\n19: в”Ӯ                         AgentCube RBAC Architecture                          в”Ӯ\\n20: в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\\n21: в”Ӯ                                                                             в”Ӯ\\n22: в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ\\n23: в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ                     ServiceAccount (SA)                             в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\\n24: в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\\n25: в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentcube-   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentd       в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ workload-manager       в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\\n26: в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ router-sa   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ controller-saв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ...\n  Line 25: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775872703328,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a42fa4d001gsb9DarL6tf3GV\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a42df94001WkdBavu3ku0xvk\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I'll create the tasks.md for AR-031:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775872703326,\"end\":1775872703326}}}\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872738293,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a42fb61001KNEQ657xoLjth1\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a42df94001WkdBavu3ku0xvk\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_fcbcd5f8f9154091805c3d90\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-031 вҖ” RBAC Configuration (SA/Role/Binding) Tasks\\n\\n**Module:** manifests  \\n**Language:** YAML (Helm)  \\n**Size:** M  \\n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Implementation Tasks\\n\\n### Phase 1: ServiceAccount Multi-Component Support (T001-T003)\\n\\n- [ ] **T001** Extend ServiceAccount template to support multiple SAs\\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/serviceaccount.yaml`\\n  - *Verify:* Template renders 3 ServiceAccounts: router-sa, agentd-controller-sa, workload-manager-sa\\n  - *Test:* `helm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube | grep -c \\\"kind: ServiceAccount\\\" # should be 3`\\n\\n- [ ] **T002** Add router ServiceAccount to values.yaml\\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\\n  - *Verify:* `rbac.serviceAccounts.router.name` exists with default value \\\"agentcube-router-sa\\\"\\n  - *Test:* Check rendered template contains \\\"agentcube-router-sa\\\"\\n\\n- [ ] **T003** Add workload-manager ServiceAccount to values.yaml\\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\\n  - *Verify:* `rbac.serviceAccounts.workloadManager.name` exists with default value \\\"agentcube-workload-manager-sa\\\"\\n  - *Test:* Check rendered template contains \\\"agentcube-workload-manager-sa\\\"\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Phase 2: ClusterRole Separation (T004-T006)\\n\\n- [ ] **T004** Create separate agentd-controller ClusterRole\\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrole-agentd.yaml` (new file)\\n  - *Verify:* Rules include pods, services, secrets, configmaps, events, CRDs, sandboxes\\n  - *Test:* `helm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube | grep \\\"kind: ClusterRole\\\" | wc -l # should be 2+`\\n\\n- [ ] **T005** Create router ClusterRole...\n  Line 29: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775872744139,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a438ef0001TcQaOlaHckZ7oU\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a438431001XnVi4W2eI9s0iG\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Created `changes/AR-031/tasks.md` with 19 atomic tasks across 7 phases:\\n\\n- **Phase 1 (T001-T003):** ServiceAccount multi-component support (3 SAs)\\n- **Phase 2 (T004-T006):** ClusterRole separation (router read-only, agentd full, workload-manager)\\n- **Phase 3 (T007-T009):** ClusterRoleBinding multi-binding\\n- **Phase 4 (T010-T011):** Namespace-scoped Role/RoleBinding\\n- **Phase 5 (T012-T013):** Helper functions for names\\n- **Phase 6 (T014-T016):** Per-component enable flags in values.yaml\\n- **Phase 7 (T017-T019):** Validation & testing\\n\\nThe LSP error