ment.yaml` дёӯжҠҪзҰ» RBAC иө„жәҗпјҲSA/ClusterRole/ClusterRoleBindingпјүиҮі `templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml`пјҢеҺҹжЁЎжқҝдҝқз•ҷ ConfigMap/Service/Deployment\\n17: - **Values жҺ§еҲ¶з»ҹдёҖпјҡ** дёәжүҖжңү RBAC иө„жәҗж·»еҠ  `values.yaml` ејҖе…іпјҡ\\n18:   - `workloadmanager.rbac.create`пјҲй»ҳи®Ө `true`пјҢдҝқжҢҒеҗ‘еҗҺе…је®№пјү\\n19:   - `router.rbac.create`пјҲе·ІеӯҳеңЁпјҢй»ҳи®Ө `false`пјү\\n20:   - `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create`пјҲй»ҳи®ӨдёҺ `volcano.scheduler.enabled` иҒ”еҠЁпјү\\n21: - **е‘ҪеҗҚи§„иҢғз»ҹдёҖпјҡ**\\n22:   - ServiceAccount: `<component>` жҲ– `agentcube-<component>`пјҲдёҺ Deployment е‘ҪеҗҚдёҖиҮҙпјү\\n23:   - ClusterRole/Role: `agentcube-<component>`пјҲж·»еҠ  `agentcube-` еүҚзјҖйҒҝе…ҚйӣҶзҫӨе‘ҪеҗҚеҶІзӘҒпјү\\n24:   - ClusterRoleBinding/RoleBinding: `agentcube-<component>-binding`\\n25: - **ж ҮзӯҫдёҖиҮҙжҖ§пјҡ** жүҖжңү RBAC иө„жәҗж·»еҠ  `app.kubernetes.io/name`, `app.kubernetes.io/instance`, `app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac` ж Үзӯҫ\\n26: - **...\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872599889,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c109fcffefKkioxaLLN9YuV\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a4162f4001ARFO1YJIa6OWoT\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a4151bd0011ShSvPuhm5LvQp\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c109fcffefKkioxaLLN9YuV\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_b10860840c9245ee82c37186\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-031: RBAC й…ҚзҪ® (SA/Role/Binding) вҖ” Design/и®ҫи®ЎиҜҙжҳҺ\\n2: \\n3: ## 1. жһ¶жһ„ (Architecture)\\n4: \\n5: ### 1.1 е®ҡдҪҚ (Purpose/Positioning)\\n6: \\n7: <!-- TODO: Describe purpose and positioning -->\\n8: \\n9: ### 1.2 еҢ…з»“жһ„ (Package Layout)\\n10: \\n11: <!-- TODO: Show directory/file layout -->\\n12: \\n13: ### 1.