":\"call_12956d3351554b689742a076\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-031: RBAC й…ҚзҪ® (SA/Role/Binding) вҖ” Delta Spec\\n\\n## Context\\n\\n- **Module:** `manifests`\\n- **Language:** YAML\\n- **Size:** M\\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`\\n\\n## Delta Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: RBAC directory consolidation\\n\\nAll RBAC resources SHALL be defined under `templates/rbac/` directory. The file `rbac-router.yaml` SHALL be moved to `templates/rbac/router.yaml`. The Volcano scheduler RBAC resources (ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding) SHALL be extracted from `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` into `templates/rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml`. The original `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` SHALL retain only non-RBAC resources (ConfigMap, Service, Deployment).\\n\\n#### Scenario: RBAC files are in the correct directory\\n- **GIVEN** the chart directory `manifests/charts/base/templates/`\\n- **WHEN** the directory listing is inspected\\n- **THEN** `rbac/` contains `workloadmanager.yaml`, `router.yaml`, and `volcano-scheduler.yaml`\\n- **AND** `rbac-router.yaml` no longer exists at the templates root\\n\\n#### Scenario: Volcano template retains only non-RBAC resources\\n- **GIVEN** `volcano.scheduler.enabled: true`\\n- **WHEN** `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` is rendered\\n- **THEN** the output contains ConfigMap, Service, and Deployment for the Volcano scheduler\\n- **AND** no ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, or ClusterRoleBinding appears from this template\\n\\n#### Scenario: Volcano RBAC renders from the new location\\n- **GIVEN** `volcano.scheduler.enabled: true`\\n- **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\\n- **THEN** the output contains ServiceAccount, ClusterRole...\n  Line 30: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775872736783,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c109fcffefKkioxaLLN9YuV\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a436513001fhUn1DNcDYcdjo\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a434515001IheNhBr34jSIlC\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c109fcffefKkioxaLLN9YuV\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The LSP errors are false positives вҖ” the YAML files contain Helm template syntax (`{{ }}`) that the YAML parser doesn't recognize. The delta-spec.md was written successfully.\\n\\nWritten `changes/AR-031/delta-spec.md` with 12 requirements and 35 GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios covering:\\n\\n1. **RBAC directory consolidation** вҖ” move `rbac-router.yaml` вҶ’ `rbac/router.yaml`, extract Volcano RBAC\\n2. **WorkloadManager RBAC values gate** вҖ” `workloadmanager.rbac.create` (default `true`)\\n3. **Volcano scheduler RBAC values gate** вҖ” `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` follows `enabled`\\n4. **Router RBAC gate unchanged** вҖ” behavior preserved after file move\\n5. **ClusterRole naming with `agentcube-` prefix** вҖ” avoid cluster-wide conflicts\\n6. **Binding naming with `-binding` suffix** вҖ” `agentcube-<component>-binding`\\n7. **ServiceAccount naming consistency** вҖ” unchanged, aligned with Deployments\\n8. **RBAC permissions unchanged** вҖ” zero changes to apiGroups/resources/verbs\\n9. **Kubernetes standard labels** вҖ” `app.kubernetes.io/name`, `instance`, `component: rbac`\\n10. **`_helpers.tpl` RBAC name helpers** вҖ” `agentcube.rbacName` and `agentcube.rbacBindingName`\\n11. **values.yaml RBAC key tree** вҖ” new keys with documented defaults\\n12. **Helm upgrade backward compatibility** вҖ” no downtime, native resource tracking\\n13. **Binding integrity** вҖ” roleRef and subjects correctly reference renamed resources\\n14. **Helm lint passes** вҖ” no errors/warnings on RBAC templates\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775872736781,\"end\":1775872736781}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-031_ST-3.log:\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872654326,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bf45f1ffeoR0P71EELxR1Ub\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a4107f1001nyKyPqnhA3PtMo\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a40f67b001pGAbNL0rHgQF4D\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285bf45f1ffeoR0P71EELxR1Ub\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_c071666bb4ed47549b8abd73\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-031 вҖ” RBAC Configuration (SA/Role/Binding)\\n\\n- **AR ID**: AR-031\\n- **Module**: manifests\\n- **Language**: YAML (Helm)\\n- **Size**: M\\n- **Status**: ST-1 Completed (design.md)\\n\\n## 1. Architecture\\n\\n### 1.1 Overview\\n\\nThe RBAC (Role-Based Access Control) configuration for AgentCube provides fine-grained permission management using Kubernetes native RBAC primitives. The implementation follows the standard Kubernetes RBAC model with ServiceAccount, Role/ClusterRole, and RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding resources.\\n\\n### 1.2 RBAC Components\\n\\n```\\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\\nв”Ӯ                         AgentCube RBAC Architecture                          в”Ӯ\\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\\nв”Ӯ                                                                             в”Ӯ\\nв”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ\\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ                     ServiceAccount (SA)                             в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\\nв”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentcube-   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ agentd       в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ