\n25: \\n26: ### AR-031-002: Controller ServiceAccount\\n27: \\n28: - **GIVEN** namespace for agentcube control plane\\n29: - **WHEN** creating ServiceAccount for controllers\\n30: - **THEN** it SHALL be named `agentcube-controller`\\n31: - **AND** SHALL be created in the agentcube-system namespace\\n32: \\n33: ---\\n34: \\n35: ## Scenario: Role Definitions\\n36: \\n37: ### AR-031-003: Agent Runtime Role\\n38: \\n39: - **GIVEN** namespace for agent deployment\\n40: - **WHEN** defining Role for agent ServiceAccount\\n41: - **THEN** it SHALL include permissions for Agent...\n  Line 28: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872524773,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c0e4f5ffelpq9u3QY0wGlKK\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a3faf20001tB5H46YW2jkZLI\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a3fa27c001k1cPo8iDuUCAbL\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c0e4f5ffelpq9u3QY0wGlKK\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_c62c2323201e4eeebca56aa7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-031: RBAC й…ҚзҪ® (SA/Role/Binding)\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\nImplement comprehensive RBAC configuration for AgentCube, defining ServiceAccounts, Roles, and RoleBindings to enable secure, least-privilege access control for agent pods and controllers across namespaces.\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n### Background\\n\\nAgentCube requires proper RBAC configuration to secure communication between its components. The current Helm chart includes basic ClusterRole/ClusterRoleBinding, but lacks:\\n- Namespace-scoped Roles for agents\\n- Dedicated ServiceAccounts for agents and controllers\\n- Granular permissions per component type\\n\\nThe delta-spec AR-031 defines specific acceptance scenarios that need implementation.\\n\\n### Goal\\n\\nCreate RBAC manifests under `manifests/rbac/` that:\\n- Define `agentcube-agent` ServiceAccount for agent pods\\n- Define `agentcube-controller` ServiceAccount for control plane\\n- Create namespace-scoped Roles with least-privilege permissions\\n- Create ClusterRole for controller with full reconciliation access\\n- Bind ServiceAccounts to appropriate Roles\\n\\n### Value\\n\\n- **Security**: Follows Kubernetes RBAC best practices with least-privilege\\n- **Isolation**: Namespace-scoped agent roles vs cluster-scoped controller roles\\n- **Maintainability**: Clear separation of concerns between agent and controller\\n- **Compliance**: Meets enterprise security requirements for multi-tenant access\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In-Scope\\n\\n| Component | Path | Description |\\n|-----------|------|-------------|\\n| Agent ServiceAccount | `manifests/rbac/agent-serviceaccount.yaml` | `agentcube-agent` SA with optional imagePullSecrets |\\n| Controller Se...\n  Line 31: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775872531949,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c0e4f5ffelpq9u3QY0wGlKK\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a4057650011Utaj4oI64Hx7p\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a40421c001VKHKNFcjcWWPoI\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c0e4f5ffelpq9u3QY0wGlKK\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Created `/changes/AR-031/proposal.md` with:\\n- **Purpose**: Background on RBAC gaps, goal to implement least-privilege SA/Role/Binding\\n- **Scope**: 8 new RBAC manifests (2 SAs, 3 Roles, 3 RoleBindings) in `manifests/rbac/`\\n- **Impact Analysis**: Dependencies (Kubernetes 1.19+, CRDs), upstream/downstream consumers, risks\\n- **Alternatives**: Compared ClusterRole-only vs extending Helm templates vs separate manifests\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775872531947,\"end\":1775872531947}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-031_ST-0.log:\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872418491,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a3ea0880010KP2MXuvo6zs2m\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a3e930e001Zyv4zDoLs04hDC\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_6dc5f9670e574cc3801b4ec4\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"mkdir -p changes/AR-031\",\"description\":\"Create AR-031 directory\"},\"output\":\"\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"\",\"exit\":0,\"description\":\"Create AR-031 directory\",\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"Create AR-031 directory\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775872418474,\"end\":1775872418489}}}}\n  Line 29: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872439856,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a3eb072001grC3AZvOprqF9J\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a3ea2e3001a0OYoOKGNH4HDB\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_815edd1c9a50450e8260281e\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Delta Spec: AR-031 вҖ” RBAC й…ҚзҪ® (SA/Role/Binding)\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing RBAC configuration (ServiceAccount, Role, RoleBinding) in the agentcube manifests module.\\n\\n## Base Specifications\\n\\n- **AR**: AR-031\\n- **Module**: `manifests`\\n- **Language**: YAML\\n- **Size**: M\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scenario: ServiceAccount Definitions\\n\\n### AR-031-001: Agent ServiceAccount\\n\\n- **GIVEN** Kubernetes namespace for agentcube components\\n- **WHEN** creating ServiceAccount for agent pods\\n- **THEN** it SHALL be named `agentcube-agent`\\n- **AND** SHALL be created in each target namespace\\n- **AND** SHALL include appropriate imagePullSecrets if needed\\n\\n### AR-031-002: Controller ServiceAccount\\n\\n- **GIVEN** namespace for agentcube control plane\\n- **WHEN** creating ServiceAccount for controllers\\n- **THEN** it SHALL be named `agentcube-controller`\\n- **AND** SHALL be created in the agentcube-system namespace\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scenario: Role Definitions\\n\\n### AR-031-003: Agent Runtime Role\\n\\n- **GIVEN** namespace for agent deployment\\n- **WHEN** defining Role for agent ServiceAccount\\n- **THEN** it SHALL include permissions for AgentRuntime CRD (get, list, watch)\\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for CodeInterpreter CRD (get, list, watch, update, patch)\\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions forPods (get, list, watch, create, delete)\\n- **AND** SHALL include permissions for Services (get, list, watch, create, update, delete)\\n- **AND** SHALL be named `agentcube-agent-runtime`\\n\\n### AR-031-004: Agent Namespace Role\\n\\n- **GIVEN** namespace for agent deployment\\n- **WHEN** defining Role for ...\n  Line 32: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872442556,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a3efe17001SeD6i6NUC226OC\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a3ef661001uN3D0L2F1X9jQe\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_27dbaa7bd6fe4803953a2e10\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"ls -la changes/AR-031/\",\"description\":\"Verify AR-031 directory\"},\"output\":\"total 16\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 09:53 .\\ndrwxr-xr-x 33 root root 4096 Apr 11 09:53 ..\\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 5167 Apr 11 09:53 delta-spec.md\\n\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"total 16\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 09:53 .\\ndrwxr-xr-x 33 root root 4096 Apr 11 09:53 ..\\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 5167 Apr 11 09:53 delta-spec.md\\n\",\"exit\":0,\"description\":\"Verify AR-031 directory\",\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"Verify AR-031 directory\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775872442538,\"end\":1775872442554}}}}\n  Line 35: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775872447140,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a3f0cc1001xSZ4s9YtJO5hZc\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a3f00ec001B7sF8D6eDtugkb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c1cf89ffectzDEDy3RAn9On\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done. Created `changes/AR-031/` directory scaffold with:\\n- `delta-spec.md` - template with RBAC scenarios for SA/Role/RoleBinding in YAML manifests\\n\\nThe delta-spec follows the same format as existing ARs with:\\n- Overview section with AR metadata (Module: manifests, Language: YAML, Siz