 container images, and Makefile-driven builds.\\n5: \\n6: ## Requirements\\n7: \\n8: ### Requirement: Helm chart installation\\n9: The system SHALL support installing/upgrading the AgentCube stack with Helm from `manifests/charts/base`, including namespace creation and values for Redis, images, replicas, and optional router RBAC.\\n10: \\n11: #### Scenario: Install with release namespace\\n12: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster and Helm 3 available\\n13: - **WHEN** the operator runs `helm upgrade --install <release> manifests/charts/base --namespace <ns> --create-namespace` with required `redis.addr` (and optional `redis.password`) plus component image overrides as needed\\n14: - **THEN** chart templates apply Workload Manager and Router workloads (and optional Volcano resources when enabled) in `<ns>` without manual editing of rendered YAML\\n15: \\n16: ### Requirement: Helm values and Redis connectivity\\n17: The system SHALL require Redis address configuration for Workload Manager and Router at runtime via chart values `redis.addr` and `redis.password` (empty password permitted when Redis has no auth).\\n18: \\n19: #### Scenario: Compon...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-031_ST-0.log:\n  Line 14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872119608,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c62e4dffe2yL2bTDMDrVotb\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a3a0e65001n9u2Mq7qLKSVmf\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a3a0698001DcRjcKjWm0cmdp\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c62e4dffe2yL2bTDMDrVotb\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_ba366fc6bf5f45b3adf42cbc\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030 вҖ” Helm Chart жЁЎжқҝдёҺ Values\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** manifests\\n4: **Language:** YAML\\n5: **Size:** L\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: Provide the complete Helm chart (`manifests/charts/base`) for deploying the AgentCube control-plane stack on Kubernetes. This includes parameterized templates for Workload Manager, Router, optional Volcano agent scheduler, RBAC resources, CRDs, and a comprehensive `values.yaml` that drives all configurable aspects (images, replicas, resources, Redis connectivity, environment overrides). The chart enables one-command installation and upgrade of AgentCube with environment-specific customization, eliminating manual YAML editing.\\n10: \\n11: ## Scope\\n12: \\n13: ### In Scope\\n14: \\n15: - `Chart.yaml` вҖ” chart metadata (`apiVersion: v1`, name `agentcube`, version `0.1.0`, appVersion `1.0.0`)\\n16: - `values.yaml` вҖ” full key tree with typed defaults for all components:\\n17:   - Global: `imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`\\n18:   - Redis: `redis.addr`, `redis.password` (empty-string defaults; user must supply at install time)\\n19:   - Router: `router.replicas`, `router.image` (repo/pullPolicy/tag), `router.service` (type/port/targetPort), `router.resources` (limits/requests), `router.config`, `router.extraEnv`, `router.serviceAccountName`, `router.rbac.create`\\n20:   - Workload Manager: `workloadmanager...\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872120964,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c62e4dffe2yL2bTDMDrVotb\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a3a13ac001w1zZlMQ5jh04Dg\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a3a0698001DcRjcKjWm0cmdp\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c62e4dffe2yL2bTDMDrVotb\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_f7a3f8666d934cb1985f1b57\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_2026