manifests/charts/base/\\n15: в”ңв”Җв”Җ Chart.yaml                              # Chart е…ғж•°жҚ® (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0)\\n16: в”ңв”Җв”Җ values.yaml                             # й»ҳи®Өй…ҚзҪ®еҖјж ‘ (Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano)\\n17: в”ңв”Җв”Җ crds/\\n18: в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml    # AgentRuntime CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\\n19: в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml # CodeInterpreter CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\\n20: в””в”Җв”Җ templates/\\n21:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ workloadmanager.yaml                # WM Deployment + Service\\n22:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ agentcube-router.yaml               # Router Deployment + Service\\n23:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ rbac/\\n24:     в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ workloadmanager.yaml            # WM ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\\n25:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ rbac-router.yaml                    # еҸҜйҖү Router ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding\\n26:     в””в”Җв”Җ volcano-agent-scheduler-development.y...\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775871003063,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a2903d3001lVz5revIaRo19g\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a28f59c001xaYdOcRgV6cI4S\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_55d13f64b5a04283b01af8e1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart жЁЎжқҝдёҺ Values вҖ” Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Context\\n4: \\n5: - **Module:** `manifests`\\n6: - **Language:** YAML\\n7: - **Size:** L\\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`, `deployment/design.md`\\n9: \\n10: ## Delta Requirements\\n11: \\n12: ### Requirement: Chart.yaml metadata\\n13: \\n14: The chart SHALL define `Chart.yaml` with `apiVersion: v1`, `name: agentcube`, `version: 0.1.0`, and `appVersion: 1.0.0`.\\n15: \\n16: #### Scenario: Chart metadata fields are correct\\n17: - **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` exists\\n18: - **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\\n19: - **THEN** `apiVersion` equals `v1`, `name` equals `agentcube`, `version` equals `0.1.0`, and `appVersion` equals `1.0.0`\\n20: \\n21: #### Scenario: Helm lint passes on chart metadata\\n22: - **GIVEN** a valid `Chart.yaml` with the fields above\\n23: - **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base` is run\\n24: - **THEN** no errors or warnings related to chart metadata are reported\\n25: \\n26: ---\\n27: \\n28: ### Requirement: values.yaml default key tree\\n29: \\n30: The chart SHALL provide a `values.yaml` with the full key tree documented in the deployment design, including typed defaults for `imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`, `redis.addr`, `redis.password`, `router` (replicas, image, service, resources, config, extraEnv, serviceAccountName, rba...\n  Line 18: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775871165207,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a294411001NEfffXuACL7mJO\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a292ba50018dfNiuStBBD0kN\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_4c715cf7fabe4a7a92360a1a\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-030 вҖ” Helm Chart жЁЎжқҝдёҺ Values вҖ” Tasks\\n\\n> **Module:** manifests\\n> **Language:** YAML\\n> **Size:** L\\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-030/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-030/design.md`, `changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md`\\n> **Dependency:** `make gen-crd` е·ІеҸҜз”ЁпјҲжҲ– CRD жүӢе·Ҙзј–еҶҷпјү\\n\\n---\\n\\n## T-001: Chart.yaml е…ғж•°жҚ®\\n\\n- [ ] T-001.01 еҲӣе»әзӣ®еҪ• `manifests/charts/base/`\\n- [ ] T-001.02 еҲӣе»ә `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml`\\n- [ ] T-001.03 и®ҫзҪ® `apiVersion: v1`\\n- [ ] T-001.04 и®ҫзҪ® `name: agentcube`\\n- [ ] T-001.05 и®ҫзҪ® `description: A Helm chart for AgentCube`\\n- [ ] T-001.06 и®ҫзҪ® `version: 0.1.0`\\n- [ ] T-001.07 и®ҫзҪ® `appVersion: 1.0.0`\\n\\n**йӘҢж”¶**: `python3 -c \\\"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml')); assert d['apiVersion']=='v1' and d['name']=='agentcube' and d['version']=='0.1.0' and d['appVersion']=='1.0.0'\\\"` ж— жҠҘй”ҷ\\n\\n---\\n\\n## T-002: values.yaml й»ҳи®ӨеҖјж ‘\\n\\n- [ ] T-002.01 еҲӣе»ә `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml`\\n- [ ] T-002.02 е®ҡд№үе…ЁеұҖй”® `imagePullSecrets: []`гҖҒ`nameOverride: \\\"\\\"`гҖҒ`fullnameOverride: \\\"\\\"`\\n- [ ] T-002.03 е®ҡд№ү `redis.addr: \\\"\\\"` е’Ң `redis.password: \\\"\\\"`пјҢеҗ«жіЁйҮҠж ҮжҳҺе®үиЈ…ж—¶еҝ…йЎ»йҖҡиҝҮ `--set` жҸҗдҫӣ\\n- [ ] T-002.04 е®ҡд№ү `router` е®Ңж•ҙй”®ж ‘пјҡ`replicas: 1`пјҢ`image.repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router`пјҢ`image.pullPolicy: IfNotPresent`пјҢ`image.tag: latest`пјҢ`service.type: ClusterIP`пјҢ`service.port: 8080`пјҢ`service.targetPort: 8080`пјҢ`resources.limits: {cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi}`пјҢ`resources.requests: {cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi}`пјҢ`config: {}`пјҢ`extraEnv: []`пјҢ`serviceAccountName: \\\"\\\"`пјҢ`rbac.create: false`\\n- [ ] T-002.05 е®ҡд№ү `workloadmanager` е®Ңж•ҙй”®ж ‘пјҡ`replicas: 1`пјҢ`image.repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadman...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-030_ST-3.log:\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775870572553,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a22735d001GIuNq3q3oeMjMd\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a225cf7001neUFjYw8W3JQWZ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_921a36c29ae94ceeafa4f373\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030 вҖ” Helm Chart жЁЎжқҝдёҺ Values\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** manifests\\n4: **Language:** YAML\\n5: **Size:** L\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: Provide the complete Helm chart (`manifests/charts/base`) for deploying the AgentCube control-plane stack on Kubernetes. This includes parameterized templates for Workload Manager, Router, optional Volcano agent scheduler, RBAC resources, CRDs, and a comprehensive `values.yaml` that drives all configurable aspects (images, replicas, resources, Redis connectivity, environment overrides). The chart enables one-command installation and upgrade of AgentCube with environment-specific customization, eliminating manual YAML editing.\\n10: \\n11: ## Scope\\n12: \\n13: ### In Scope\\n14: \\n15: - `Chart.yaml` вҖ” chart metadata (`apiVersion: v1`, name `agentcube`, version `0.1.0`, appVersion `1.0.0`)\\n16: - `values.yaml` вҖ” full key tree with typed defaults for all components:\\n17:   - Global: `imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`\\n18:   - Redis: `redis.addr`, `redis.password` (empty-string defaults; user must supply at install time)\\n19:   - Router: `router.replicas`, `router.image` (repo/pullPolicy/tag), `router.service` (type/port/targetPort), `router.resources` (limits/requests), `router.config`, `router.extraEnv`, `router.serviceAccountName`, `router.rbac.create`\\n20:   - Workload Manager: `workloadmanager...\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775870573904,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a227892001KXG5g79mH7U27c\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a225cf7001neUFjYw8W3JQWZ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_02d88ecb65344f6fb2b71c85\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart жЁЎжқҝдёҺ Values вҖ” Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Context\\n4: \\n5: - **Module:** `manifests`\\n6: - **Language:** YAML\\n7: - **Size:** L\\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`, `deployment/design.md`\\n9: \\n10: ## Delta Requirements\\n11: \\n12: ### Requirement: Chart.yaml metadata\\n13: \\n14: The chart SHALL define `Chart.yaml` with `apiVersion: v1`, `name: agentcube`, `version: 0.1.0`, and `appVersion: 1.0.0`.\\n15: \\n16: #### Scenario: Chart metadata fields are correct\\n17: - **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` exists\\n18: - **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\\n19: - **THEN** `apiVersion` equals `v1`, `name` equals `agentcube`, `version` equals `0.1.0`, and `appVersion` equals `1.0.0`\\n20: \\n21: #### Scenario: Helm lint passes on chart metadata\\n22: - **GIVEN** a valid `Chart.yaml` with the fields above\\n23: - **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base` is run\\n24: - **THEN** no errors or warnings related to chart metadata are reported\\n25: \\n26: ---\\n27: \\n28: ### Requirement: values.yaml default key tree\\n29: \\n30: The chart SHALL provide a `values.yaml` with the full key tree documented in the deployment design, including typed defaults for `imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`, `redis.addr`, `redis.password`, `router` (replicas, image, service, resources, config, extraEnv, serviceAccountName, rba...\n  Line 20: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775870832537,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a2375f0001UcH5Z7Cye06jiB\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a235e00001cLpCk1gWA66RUJ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e13ecaffeMp9o3UxFFIXU67\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_8761772f375343018f96da17\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-030: Helm Chart жЁЎжқҝдёҺ Values вҖ” Design/и®ҫи®ЎиҜҙжҳҺ\\n\\n## 1. жһ¶жһ„ (Architecture)\\n\\n### 1.1 е®ҡдҪҚ (Purpose/Positioning)\\n\\n`manifests/charts/base` жҳҜ AgentCube жҺ§еҲ¶йқўж Ҳзҡ„ Helm ChartпјҢжҸҗдҫӣеҸӮж•°еҢ–зҡ„ Kubernetes иө„жәҗжЁЎжқҝпјҢж”ҜжҢҒдёҖй”®е®үиЈ…гҖҒеҚҮзә§е’Ңеӣһж»ҡгҖӮChart й©ұеҠЁ Workload ManagerгҖҒRouterгҖҒеҸҜйҖү Volcano и°ғеәҰеҷЁзҡ„е®Ңж•ҙйғЁзҪІз”ҹе‘Ҫе‘ЁжңҹпјҢйҖҡиҝҮ `values.yaml` йӣҶдёӯз®ЎзҗҶжүҖжңүеҸҜй…ҚзҪ®еҸӮж•°пјҲй•ңеғҸгҖҒеүҜжң¬ж•°гҖҒиө„жәҗй…ҚйўқгҖҒRedis иҝһжҺҘгҖҒзҺҜеўғеҸҳйҮҸиҰҶзӣ–пјүгҖӮ\\n\\nChart жҳҜ E2E жөӢиҜ•гҖҒз”ҹдә§йғЁзҪІгҖҒејҖеҸ‘иҖ…жң¬ең° Kind йӣҶзҫӨзҡ„з»ҹдёҖе…ҘеҸЈпјҢж¶ҲйҷӨжүӢеҠЁзј–иҫ‘ YAML зҡ„йңҖжұӮгҖӮ\\n\\n### 1.2 еҢ…з»“жһ„ (Package Layout)\\n\\n```\\nmanifests/charts/base/\\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ Chart.yaml                              # Chart е…ғж•°жҚ® (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0)\\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ values.yaml                             # й»ҳи®Өй…ҚзҪ®еҖјж ‘ (Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano)\\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ crds/\\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml    # AgentRuntime CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml # CodeInterpreter CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\\nв””в”Җв”Җ templates/\\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ workloadmanager.yaml                # WM Deployment + Service\\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ agentcube-router.yaml               # Router Deployment + Service\\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ rbac/\\n    в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ workloadmanager.yaml            # WM ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ rbac-router.yaml                    # еҸҜйҖү Router ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding\\n    в””в”Җв”Җ volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # еҸҜйҖү Volcano и°ғеәҰеҷЁе…ЁеҘ—иө„жәҗ\\n```\\n\\n### 1.3 дҫқиө–е…ізі» (Dependencies)\\n\\n```\\nHelm Chart (manifests/charts/base)\\n  в”ңв”Җв”Җ еӨ–йғЁдҫқиө–\\n  в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ Helm 3                          # Chart жү“еҢ…дёҺе®үиЈ…\\n  в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ Kubernetes 1.28+                # CRD жіЁеҶҢгҖҒDeployment/Service/RBAC еҲӣе»ә\\n  в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ Redis/Valkey (еӨ–йғЁе®һдҫӢ)          # ең°еқҖе’ҢеҜҶз ҒйҖҡиҝҮ values жҸҗдҫӣ\\n  в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ agent-sandbox CRDs (еӨ–йғЁ)        # WM ClusterRole еј•з”Ё agents...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-030_ST-2.log:\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775870175084,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a1c62f5001KxuPWt0xPuwYTS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a1c4f90001PkaJUP8it1GON0\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_d4eafb2fc7394ce59f265184\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030 вҖ” Helm Chart жЁЎжқҝдёҺ Values\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** manifests\\n4: **Language:** YAML\\n5: **Size:** L\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: Provide the complete Helm chart (`manifests/charts/base`) for deploying the AgentCube control-plane stack on Kubernetes. This includes parameterized templates for Workload Manager, Router, optional Volcano agent scheduler, RBAC resources, CRDs, and a comprehensive `values.yaml` that drives all configurable aspects (images, replicas, resources, Redis connectivity, environment overrides). The chart enables one-command installation and upgrade of AgentCube with environment-specific customization, eliminating manual YAML editing.\\n10: \\n11: ## Scope\\n12: \\n13: ### In Scope\\n14: \\n15: - `Chart.yaml` вҖ” chart metadata (`apiVersion: v1`, name `agentcube`, version `0.