e> manifests/charts/base --namespace <ns> --create-namespace` with required `redis.addr` (and optional `redis.password`) plus component image overrides as needed\\n14: - **THEN** chart templates apply Workload Manager and Router workloads (and optional Volcano resources when enabled) in `<ns>` without manual editing of rendered YAML\\n15: \\n16: ### Requirement: Helm values and Redis connectivity\\n17: The system SHALL require Redis address configuration for Workload Manager and Router at runtime via chart values `redis.addr` and `redis.password` (empty password permitted when Redis has no auth).\\n18: \\n19: #### Scenario: Components receive Redis ...\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775870317176,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a1ca38f0019Ji0XKvCVS8yO0\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a1c8551001VW6oBa0SXjW305\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_70847bf165644986b2e19add\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-030: Helm Chart жЁЎжқҝдёҺ Values вҖ” Delta Spec\\n\\n## Context\\n\\n- **Module:** `manifests`\\n- **Language:** YAML\\n- **Size:** L\\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`, `deployment/design.md`\\n\\n## Delta Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Chart.yaml metadata\\n\\nThe chart SHALL define `Chart.yaml` with `apiVersion: v1`, `name: agentcube`, `version: 0.1.0`, and `appVersion: 1.0.0`.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Chart metadata fields are correct\\n- **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` exists\\n- **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\\n- **THEN** `apiVersion` equals `v1`, `name` equals `agentcube`, `version` equals `0.1.0`, and `appVersion` equals `1.0.0`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Helm lint passes on chart metadata\\n- **GIVEN** a valid `Chart.yaml` with the fields above\\n- **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base` is run\\n- **THEN** no errors or warnings related to chart metadata are reported\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 