”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\\n17: в”Ӯ   Client    в”Ӯ в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв–ә   в”Ӯ   Router    в”Ӯ\\n18: в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ                           в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\\n19:      в–І                                            в”Ӯ\\n20:      в”Ӯ                                            в”Ӯ JWT Token\\n21:      в”Ӯ                                            в”Ӯ (Signed with Router Keys)\\n22:      в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\\n23:                                   ...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-023_ST-7.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775864567259,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286393f55ffe5cb8pHqVc20fEy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79c6d25e0013Lkoc8iq4vAS4j\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79c6c1840013Fv0WPUBLsJwvS\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286393f55ffe5cb8pHqVc20fEy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"toolu_153e19189b024c138870b7a7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark\",\"pattern\":\"AR-023\"},\"output\":\"Found 134 matches (showing first 100)\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-023_ST-6.log:\\n  Line 38: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1775864559739,\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_2863a8e69ffehRilhpu9IffRAw\\\",\\\"part\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"prt_d79c6a4f9001asbS2ROMr1Qr3P\\\",\\\"messageID\\\":\\\"msg_d79c681b7001eHDZaAjEwq7z5a\\\",\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_2863a8e69ffehRilhpu9IffRAw\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"## Verification Results for AR-023 вҖ” CLI invoke/status е‘Ҫд»Ө\\\\n\\\\n### Summary: вң… SPEC COMPLIANT, 103/103 tests passing\\\\n\\\\n| Spec Requirement | Status |\\\\n|------------------|--------|\\\\n| **Pack